            <title>[SOLR-1767] DataImportHandler: dataimporter.functions.escapeSql() does not escape backslash character</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SOLR-1767</link>
                <project id="12310230" key="SOLR">Solr</project>
